{
  "texts": [
    "As measure of coverage across all benchmarked datasets, we used the mapping coverage as reported by mosdepth 65 (version 0.3.2), which was averaged across all autosomes.",
    "In addition to GIAB's HG002 sample, we also benchmarked SV on three assemblies from 1000 Genomes (HG01243, HG02055 and HG02080).",
    "Here, we leveraged the phased HiFi assemblies provided at https://github.com/human-pangenomics/hpgp-data and the corresponding long reads.",
    "The benchmark set was derived from a dipcall 66 (version 0.2) alignment against the GRCh38 reference.",
    "This result was used together with the corresponding BED files for benchmarking 67."
  ]
}